  "original_title": "\u0dc0\u0dd3 \u0d9c\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dc5 \u0db8\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dbd \u0db4\u0dbb\u0dab \u0dab\u0dba\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0dc4\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dc0\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dc5 \u0db4\u0dbd\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dc0\u0dca\u0dc0 \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0db3\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The amount set aside to be paid off is settled against an old loan",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Ministry of Agriculture, the amount of 250 million rupees that was to be paid to the farmers for the stock of paddy purchased by the Paddy Marketing Board was released today.",
        "This amount allocated for payment to the farmers had been offset against the old loan by a state bank.",
        "Due to the problematic situation, the payment to the farmers was delayed by several days.",
        "Due to this situation, the payments to the farmers who were given rice were also delayed and the Minister of Agriculture Mahinda Amaraweera had informed the farmers that the problems would be solved and the payments would be processed very soon.",
        "Agriculture Minister Mahinda Amaraweera, President's Secretary Saman Ekanayake, President's Chief of Staff Sagala Ratnayake have intervened to solve this problem."
      ],
      "title_ents": [],
      "body_line_ents_list": [
        [
          {
            "text": "the Ministry of Agriculture",
            "label": "ORG"
          },
          {
            "text": "250 million",
